OL,3,CJersey to protect more of its waters
OL,4,Cfrom fishing practices
OL,6,FJersey's States Assembly has
OL,7,Funanimously approved an expansion of
OL,8,Fthe island's Marine Protected Areas
OL,9,F(MPAs).
OL,11,FIn the vote on Thursday, politicians
OL,12,Fagreed to quadruple the area of its
OL,13,Fwaters protected from some fishing
OL,14,Fpractices, including trawling and
OL,15,Fdredging.
OL,17,FAt the moment, only 6.5% of the
OL,18,Fisland's waters are currently
OL,19,Fprotected from mobile fishing gear.
OL,20,FStarting in September, the new MPA
OL,21,Fwill cover 21.7% of the waters.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
