OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773504677
OL,3,CJersey to protect more of its waters
OL,4,Cfrom fishing practices
OL,6,FAn additional 1.9% of Jersey's waters
OL,7,Fwill then be protected in 2030.
OL,9,FThe expansion of the MPA means that
OL,10,FJersey is ahead of England, where
OL,11,Faround 11% of its seas are afforded
OL,12,Fequivalent protection.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
