OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773504677
OL,3,CJersey to protect more of its waters
OL,4,Cfrom fishing practices
OL,6,FSpeaking in the States, Environment
OL,7,FMinister, Deputy Steve Luce, said: "By
OL,8,Fgradually and systematically moving
OL,9,Fdredging and trawling out of our
OL,10,Fshallow, productive habitats, we'll
OL,11,Fpreserve nursery grounds and increase
OL,12,Ffish stocks, both for boats and the
OL,13,Fdivers and potters that can access the
OL,14,Fareas without the same impact."
OL,16,FDeputy Hilary Jeune, Chair of Jersey's
OL,17,FEnvironment, Housing and
OL,18,FInfrastructure Panel, told ITV News
OL,19,Fshe was pleased with the outcome:
OL,20,F"This is a fantastic step and a great
OL,21,Fstart, but we can do more".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
