PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773504677
OL,3,CJersey to protect more of its waters
OL,4,Cfrom fishing practices
OL,6,FDeputy Jeune and other members of the
OL,7,FScrutiny Panel had hoped that the
OL,8,FEnvironment Minister would commit to
OL,9,Fthe '30 by 30' initiative, which would
OL,10,Fsee 30% of the island's waters
OL,11,Fprotected by 2030 - a target that
OL,12,Fcould still be reached.
OL,14,FShe also said that politicians need to
OL,15,Fwork with the fishing community to
OL,16,Fensure their livelihoods are protected.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
