OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1773504677
OL,3,CJersey to protect more of its waters
OL,4,Cfrom fishing practices
OL,6,F"I think it's important that the
OL,7,F(Environment) Minister said, that he
OL,8,Fneeds to put forward financial support
OL,9,Ffor diversification, for looking into
OL,10,Fmore sustainable fishing methods, and
OL,11,Fseeing that long-term sustainability
OL,12,Fof the fishing community."
OL,14,FDeputy Luce said in the States on
OL,15,FThursday that he was looking at a
OL,16,F"future fisheries project".
