OL,3,CJersey to protect more of its waters
OL,4,Cfrom fishing practices
OL,6,FHe said: "We very much hope we're
OL,7,Fgoing to be able to identify for the
OL,8,Ffleet ways of adding value to all the
OL,9,Fproducts they sell, which means they
OL,10,Fcan catch less and make more money".
